quantifies the area occupied by TH stained and TH unstained nerves
carries out shift of origin for the nerve areas (stained and unstained) relative to the lumen
calculates the angle relative to the lumen
converts the angles in rad to deg
generates the quadrants based on an anatomical key
counts area of unstained and stained nerves per quadrant
converts the values from sq microns to sq mm
rounds of the sq mm
calculates the % of TH pos and TH neg as a function of the total nerve tissue
